Text: FIRST NOTICE Assessment ResultsOne or more people have evaluated your performance as a boss at ImproveNowcom The results have been compiled and are strictly confidential for your eyes only You may review your results by logging on to a secure passwordprotected area of our site at assessmentsIYBossBossResults Your login is Your password is otg If you have login problems go to faqsindexcfmactionresultsfaqs We trust that your employees chose to participate in this process in a spirit of constructive criticism and we are committed to supporting the possibility of positive change in your organization Accordingly you will find that your results link to a customized list of resources weve recommended to improve your performance in key areas And if you believe that simply letting your people know that youre listening to them that you care about their opinions and that you intend to change things for the better can have a profound effect on morale we recommend you initiate a topdown assessment It takes only a minute and can be done at AssessmentsIYBossindexcfmactiontopdown To find out more about ImproveNowcom including instructions on how to invite other employees to join in your assessment click here If you have any questions about the assessment process or about our organization in general please check out faqsindexcfmactionmanagementfaqs or contact us at mailto mproveNowcom This is a complimentary service of ImproveNowcom Thank you James S Povec CEO ImproveNowcom
